Document: VisualShaderNodeScreenUVToSDF
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodescreenuvtosdf.rst
Summary: Translates to screen_uv_to_sdf(uv) in shaders, using SCREEN_UV if UV port is unconnected.

Translates to screen_uv_to_sdf(uv) in the shader language. If the UV port isn't connected, SCREEN_UV is used instead.